671
00:36:53,296 --> 00:36:56,546
Scott: Sometimes something doesn't make complete sense in one spot or another.

672
00:36:56,566 --> 00:36:59,229
Scott: This is freaking polished.

673
00:36:59,290 --> 00:37:04,506
Scott: It's as if he wrote the whole thing and double checked everything and made sure it was all perfect.

674
00:37:05,314 --> 00:37:11,480
